293
00:19:38,530 --> 00:19:41,175
Dia ada ambil kesempatan?

294
00:19:41,300 --> 00:19:43,189
Berhenti mengarut dan pergi.

295
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:44,695
Sakitlah, tak guna!

