Awak tak perlu berpura-pura.

378
00:25:11,950 --> 00:25:13,145
Hye-ji, mari makan malam.

379
00:25:13,360 --> 00:25:15,125
- Tak apalah.
- Marilah.

380
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,279
